<h1>BIS：必须加强监管以防止更多银行倒闭 (Free Version)</h1>
<p>Authors: ['劳拉•努南']</p>
<p>Publisher: 英国《金融时报》</p>
<p>Time: 2023-06-02T00:53:13+00:00</p>
<p>Published Time: 2023-06-01T12:00:99+08:00</p>
